Raymond Dakim Harris Joiner 514P13-5 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 18, 2016 Raymond Joiner, for Joiner, Raymond Dakim Harris. Ryan Frank Haigh, Special Deputy Attorney General, James R. O'Neill, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 5th of May 2016 by Defendant to Dismiss for Lack of Territorial Jurisdiction:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 18th of August 2016."
